.TH "libnvmf_discovery_args_create" 9 "libnvmf_discovery_args_create" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvmf_discovery_args_create \- Allocate a discovery args object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvmf_discovery_args_create
.BI "(struct libnvmf_discovery_args **argsp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "argsp" 12
On success, set to the newly allocated object
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates and initialises a \fIstruct libnvmf_discovery_args\fP with sensible
defaults. The caller must release it with \fBlibnvmf_discovery_args_free\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or a negative error code on failure.
